                                    include the rate/salary offered to you so please refer to that letter for further
                                    details. As part of our ongoing commitment to fostering career growth, PBS offers an
                                    automatic 5% annual raise to non-exempt employees on their employment anniversary
                                    date. This raise is applied each year for up to five years. The goal of this program
